en_174957_0	Erecting of a fence to a distance 4,750 meters to prevent accidents by falling into Viyaana Canal, has been completed.
en_174957_1	Several lives were lost during the past after vehicles fell into Viyaana Canal in Maiyanganaya.
en_174957_2	President Maithripala Sirisena ordered to erect a fence immediately to prevent the accidents.
en_174957_3	Accordingly a steel fence at a cost of 52 million rupee has been erected by the sides of the Loggal Oya on the Badulla â€“ Maiyanganaya main road and by the sides of the Viyaana Canal.
en_174957_4	The Road Development Authority implemented the project.
